drawings.author: ZWZhNTMzZTE2NzI3
drawings.text: 2 guards guard each of the four City of the dead entrances. These are placed here in case the DM chooses to get those involved.

drawings.author: ZWZhNTMzZTE2NzI3
drawings.text: Below is Sir Ambrose Everdawn. If creeping at night, characters have a 30 percent chance of running into him. He attempts to escort them out and alerts guards if the party refuses.

drawings.author: ZWZhNTMzZTE2NzI3
drawings.text: These crawling claws are guarding Uld Brandath's remains

drawings.author: ZWZhNTMzZTE2NzI3
drawings.text: The above staircase is hidden from the players until such time as they identify the illusion. Once they do, unhide the staircase.
